{"tid":1880990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[奶共要還架]期待中國遊客訪日引起質疑　安倍新春賀詞被刪除","createTime":"2020-02-15T08:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T09:08:51.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"98d08cecaeb5b3b0536c2cec995cf09b44eaa64a","tid":1880990,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"日本駐華大使館在官方網站，刪除首相安倍晉三在新年賀詞中，指期待中國遊客訪日的內容。<br />\n<br />\n賀詞上月24日公布在網站，安倍在賀詞中，邀請中國人在春節假期期間及東京奧運期間，到日本旅遊，表示期待大量中國遊客到訪日本，但當時中國的新型肺炎疫情已經擴大，引起民眾質疑，日本外務省後來致歉，指賀詞不合時宜，並於六日後删除。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508754-20200215.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508754-20200215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNtMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=e6827126\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508754-20200215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3fe89f69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508754-20200215.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6dd713e44411685e5bdf1a8d165928fd1c87b893","tid":1880990,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"要俾人屌先做嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e3a4be4b355fc1550f34cbef0b5729dc09f7fc","tid":1880990,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"見錢眼開連命都唔要。"}]}